(103, 103, 'ar', 'Bose SoundSport, Wireless Earbuds, (Sweatproof Bluetooth Headphones)', '<h1 id=\"title\" class=\"a-size-large a-spacing-none\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span id=\"productTitle\" class=\"a-size-large\">Bose SoundSport, Wireless Earbuds</span></h1>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"a-size-large\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/storage/media/1QTwUWAaA36Tgw9LgWaI2fApRHzve9N6MJ3HjDMl.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1464\" height=\"600\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"a-size-large\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/szTXcgsGlNI\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/storage/media/P9j8oj9bzXHDW8Yx0JJLvxXRDavjhG3CKACKXlSD.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1464\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/storage/media/sRpYNFVfiaOcwp5AfLxW2zmp1sAs6AEXnM8IlW4i.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1 class=\"aplus-h1 aplus-module-1-heading a-text-bold\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Nothing to lose.</h1>\r\n<p class=\"aplus-p2 aplus-module-1-description\" style=\"text-align: center;\">The Bose Connect app makes it easier to connect and switch between devices.</p>\r\n<p class=\"aplus-p2 aplus-module-1-description\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Personalize your settings so you can power your workout quickly and easily.</p>\r\n<p class=\"aplus-p2 aplus-module-1-description\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Tile makes it easy to find your headphones if they ever go missing.</p>\r\n<p class=\"aplus-p2 aplus-module-1-description\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Use the Bose Connect app to update your headphones&rsquo; software, then download</p>\r\n<p class=\"aplus-p2 aplus-module-1-description\" style=\"text-align: center;\">the Tile app and follow the instructions. And you&rsquo;ll never lose your music.</p>\r\n<p class=\"aplus-p2 aplus-module-1-description\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\" border=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\"><img src=\"/storage/media/NQjdR4HjIY5AmPvqfLvzffY26VKU1X2fMVQG8Rnh.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" /></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\r\n<h1 class=\"aplus-h1 aplus-module-1-heading a-text-bold\" style=\"text-align: center;\">The only challenge left is your workout.</h1>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"default\"><strong>Product description:</strong></p>\r\n<div id=\"productDescription\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-small\">\r\n<div class=\"disclaim\">Color:<strong>Black</strong></div>\r\n<p>With no wires in the way, Bose Sound Sport wireless headphones keep you moving with powerful audio and Stay Hear+ tips designed for comfort and stability. A soft silicone material and unique shape provide a secure fit that stays put and feels good. Connect to your device easily with Bluetooth and NFC pairing, and use the inline mic and remote to control volume, skip tracks and take calls.</p>\r\n<p>With the Bose Connect app, controlling and switching between multiple devices is easy. These headphones are sweat and weather resistant and have a lithium ion battery that delivers up to 6 hours per charge. With performance like this, the only challenge left is your workout.</p>\r\n<p>Included: Sound Sport wireless headphones; Stay Hear+ tips; USB charging cable; carry case. Allow up to two hours to fully charge the battery. A full charge powers the headphones for up to six hours. The headphones will not play while charging.</p>\r\n<p>Note: Before charging, be sure the headphones are at room temperature between 41 degree Fahrenheit (5 degree Celsius ) and 104 degree Fahrenheit (40 degree Celsius ). &ldquo;Made for iPod,&rdquo; &ldquo;Made for iPhone,&rdquo; and &ldquo;Made for iPad&rdquo; mean that an electronic accessory has been designed to connect specifically to iPod, iPhone, or iPad, respectively, and has been certified by the developer to meet Apple performance standards.</p>\r\n<p>Apple is not responsible for the operation of this device or its compliance with safety and regulatory standards. Please note that the use of this accessory with iPod, iPhone or iPad may affect wireless performance</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Product information:</strong></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"a-size-large\">Color:<strong>Black</strong></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"a-row a-spacing-top-base\">\r\n<div class=\"a-column a-span6\">\r\n<div class=\"a-row a-spacing-base\">\r\n<div class=\"a-section table-padding\">\r\n<table id=\"productDetails_detailBullets_sections1\" class=\"a-keyvalue prodDetTable\" role=\"presentation\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"a-color-secondary a-size-base prodDetSectionEntry\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Product Dimensions</th>\r\n<td class=\"a-size-base\" style=\"text-align: right;\">1 x 1.2 x 1.2 inches</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"a-color-secondary a-size-base prodDetSectionEntry\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Item Weight</th>\r\n<td class=\"a-size-base\" style=\"text-align: right;\">0.8 ounces</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"a-color-secondary a-size-base prodDetSectionEntry\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Shipping Weight</th>\r\n<td class=\"a-size-base\" style=\"text-align: right;\">12.6 ounces</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"a-color-secondary a-size-base prodDetSectionEntry\" style=\"text-align: left;\">ASIN</th>\r\n<td class=\"a-size-base\" style=\"text-align: right;\">B01L7PSJFO</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"a-color-secondary a-size-base prodDetSectionEntry\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Item model number</th>\r\n<td class=\"a-size-base\" style=\"text-align: right;\">761529-0010</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"a-color-secondary a-size-base prodDetSectionEntry\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Batteries</th>\r\n<td class=\"a-size-base\" style=\"text-align: right;\">1 Lithium Metal batteries required. (included)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'A high quality audio experience, consistently balanced at any volume, thanks to Bose active EQ. Connectivity Technology: Wireless\r\nWireless convenience, with easy Bluetooth and NFC pairing aided by voice prompts\r\nExclusive Stay Hear and tips keep the headphones comfortably in place during workouts'),
(104, 104, 'ar', 'Powerbeats3 Wireless In-Ear Headphones - Black', '<h1 id=\"title\" class=\"a-size-large a-spacing-none\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span id=\"productTitle\" class=\"a-size-large\">Powerbeats3 Wireless In-Ear Headphones - Black</span></h1>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id=\"descriptionAndDetails\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-extra-large\">\r\n<div id=\"productDescription_feature_div\" class=\"celwidget\" data-feature-name=\"productDescription\" data-cel-widget=\"productDescription_feature_div\">\r\n<div id=\"productDescription_feature_div\" class=\"a-row feature\" data-feature-name=\"productDescription\" data-template-name=\"productDescription\" data-cel-widget=\"productDescription_feature_div\">\r\n<p class=\"default\"><strong>Product description:</strong></p>\r\n<div id=\"productDescription\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-small\">\r\n<p>In-Ear Stereo Headphones, Connect via Class 1 Bluetooth with your device for wireless workout freedom, Includes 4 sets of eartips, case and Micro USB charging cable</p>\r\n<p>Up to 12 hours of battery life to power through multiple workouts, With Fast Fuel, a 5-minute charge gives you 1 hour of playback when battery is low, Sweat and water resistance to handle tough training</p>\r\n<p>Take calls, control your music and activate Siri with RemoteTalk, Rechargeable Lithium-Ion battery</p>\r\n<p>Simultaneously connect to your Apple Watch, iPad and Mac (requires iCloud account and macOS Sierra, iOS 10, or watchOS 3)</p>\r\n<p>Flexible, secure-fit earhooks maximize comfort and stability, Dynamic, high-performance sound pushes you to the next level</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Product information:</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"a-row a-spacing-top-base\">\r\n<div class=\"a-column a-span6\">\r\n<div class=\"a-row a-spacing-base\">\r\n<div class=\"a-section table-padding\">\r\n<table id=\"productDetails_detailBullets_sections1\" class=\"a-keyvalue prodDetTable\" style=\"width: 504px;\" role=\"presentation\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"a-color-secondary a-size-base prodDetSectionEntry\" style=\"width: 156.542px; text-align: left;\">Product Dimensions</th>\r\n<td class=\"a-size-base\" style=\"width: 317.875px; text-align: right;\">8.3 x 2.5 x 2.7 inches</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"a-color-secondary a-size-base prodDetSectionEntry\" style=\"width: 156.542px; text-align: left;\">Item Weight</th>\r\n<td class=\"a-size-base\" style=\"width: 317.875px; text-align: right;\">3.52 ounces</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"a-color-secondary a-size-base prodDetSectionEntry\" style=\"width: 156.542px; text-align: left;\">Shipping Weight</th>\r\n<td class=\"a-size-base\" style=\"width: 317.875px; text-align: right;\">5.6 ounces&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"a-color-secondary a-size-base prodDetSectionEntry\" style=\"width: 156.542px; text-align: left;\">Manufacturer</th>\r\n<td class=\"a-size-base\" style=\"width: 317.875px; text-align: right;\">Beats</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"a-color-secondary a-size-base prodDetSectionEntry\" style=\"width: 156.542px; text-align: left;\">ASIN</th>\r\n<td class=\"a-size-base\" style=\"width: 317.875px; text-align: right;\">B06X979GGB</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"a-color-secondary a-size-base prodDetSectionEntry\" style=\"width: 156.542px; text-align: left;\">California residents</th>\r\n<td class=\"a-size-base\" style=\"width: 317.875px; text-align: right;\">&nbsp;for Proposition 65 warning</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"a-color-secondary a-size-base prodDetSectionEntry\" style=\"width: 156.542px; text-align: left;\">Item model number</th>\r\n<td class=\"a-size-base\" style=\"width: 317.875px; text-align: right;\">ML8V2LL/A</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"a-color-secondary a-size-base prodDetSectionEntry\" style=\"width: 156.542px; text-align: left;\">Batteries</th>\r\n<td class=\"a-size-base\" style=\"width: 317.875px; text-align: right;\">1 Lithium ion batteries required.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"renewedProgramDescriptionBtf_feature_div\" class=\"celwidget\" data-feature-name=\"renewedProgramDescriptionBtf\" data-cel-widget=\"renewedProgramDescriptionBtf_feature_div\"></div>', 'Up to 12 hours of battery life to power through multiple workouts\r\nWith Fast Fuel, a 5-minute charge gives you 1 hour of playback when battery is low');
