(105, 105, 'ar', 'Beats Solo3 Wireless On-Ear Headphones - Apple W1 Headphone Chip, Class 1 Bluetooth', '<h1 id=\"title\" class=\"a-size-large a-spacing-none\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span id=\"productTitle\" class=\"a-size-large\">Beats Solo3 Wireless On-Ear Headphones</span></h1>\r\n<h1 class=\"a-size-large a-spacing-none\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</h1>\r\n<h1 class=\"a-size-large a-spacing-none\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span id=\"productTitle\" class=\"a-size-large\"><img src=\"/storage/media/BkpYICatCTYVIc1i5UOpeBgaINVwU7Z5Tm5YdsVr.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"798\" /></span></h1>\r\n<h1 class=\"a-size-large a-spacing-none\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span id=\"productTitle\" class=\"a-size-large\"><img src=\"/storage/media/RMw6BsYDUeEfKW18FpoTbYWnb41iiTA8ecOzW9WH.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"668\" /></span></h1>\r\n<h1 class=\"a-size-large a-spacing-none\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span id=\"productTitle\" class=\"a-size-large\"><img src=\"/storage/media/DXUBrN8dfILWEwLsXkTb9GOvsNgkOJMQpJLbPvJY.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"617\" /></span></h1>\r\n<h1 class=\"a-size-large a-spacing-none\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span id=\"productTitle\" class=\"a-size-large\"><img src=\"/storage/media/BBy8URh2gouiiycE3CbQB8KckC39VKZJWdnDsDEx.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"600\" /></span></h1>\r\n<h1 class=\"a-size-large a-spacing-none\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</h1>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-large a-spacing-none\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span class=\"a-size-large\">Product Details:</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-large a-spacing-none\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-none\">\r\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">High-performance wireless Bluetooth headphones in black</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">Features the Apple W1 chip and Class 1 wireless Bluetooth connectivity</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">With up to 40 hours of battery life, Beats Solo3 wireless is your perfect everyday headphone</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">Compatible with iOS and Android devices</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">With Fast Fuel, 5 minutes of charging gives you 3 hours of playback when battery is low</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">Adjustable fit with comfort-cushioned ear cups made for everyday use</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">Sleek, streamlined design that&rsquo;s durable and foldable to go everywhere you do</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"a-row a-expander-container a-expander-inline-container\" aria-live=\"polite\">\r\n<div class=\"a-expander-content a-expander-extend-content a-expander-content-expanded\" aria-expanded=\"true\">\r\n<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-none\">\r\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">Take calls, control your music, and activate Siri with the multifunction on-ear controls</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">The award-winning sound and design you&rsquo;ve come to love from Beats, with premium playback with fine-tuned acoustics that maximize clarity, breadth, and balance</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">What&rsquo;s in the Box: Beats Solo3 Wireless Headphones, Carrying Case, Universal USB charging cable (USB-A to USB Micro-B), Quick Start Guide, Warranty Card</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"a-row\">\r\n<div class=\"a-column a-span6\">\r\n<p class=\"a-size-medium a-spacing-small\"><strong>Technical Details:</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-medium a-spacing-small\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a-expander-content a-expander-extend-content\" aria-expanded=\"true\">\r\n<div class=\"a-row a-expander-container a-expander-inline-container\" aria-live=\"polite\">\r\n<div class=\"a-expander-content a-expander-section-content a-section-expander-inner\" aria-expanded=\"true\">\r\n<table id=\"productDetails_tec