(207, 188, 'ar', 'Oppo Reno4 - 6.4-inch 128GB/8GB Dual SIM 4G Mobile Phone - Mo Salah Edition', '<p><strong>Network</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Technology</strong>: GSM / HSPA / LTE</li>\r\n<li><strong>2G bands</strong>: GSM 850 / 900 / 1800 / 1900 - SIM 1 and SIM 2</li>\r\n<li><strong>3G bands</strong>: HSDPA 850 / 900 / 1900 / 2100</li>\r\n<li><strong>4G bands</strong>: LTE</li>\r\n<li><strong>Speed</strong>: HSPA 42.2/5.76 Mbps, LTE-A</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Body</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Dimensions</strong>: 160.3 x 73.9 x 7.7 mm</li>\r\n<li><strong>Weight</strong>: 165 g</li>\r\n<li><strong>Build</strong>: Glass front, plastic back, plastic frame</li>\r\n<li><strong>SIM</strong>: Dual SIM (Nano-SIM, dual stand-by)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Display</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Type</strong>: Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n<li><strong>Size</strong>: 6.4 inches, 98.9 cm2&nbsp;(~83.5% screen-to-Body ratio)</li>\r\n<li><strong>Resolution</strong>: 1080 x 2400 pixels, 20:9 ratio (~411 ppi density)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Platform</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>OS</strong>: Android 10, ColorOS 7.2</li>\r\n<li><strong>Chipset</strong>: Qualcomm SM7125 Snapdragon 720G (8 nm)</li>\r\n<li><strong>CPU</strong>: Octa-core (2x2.3 GHz Kryo 465 Gold and 6x1.8 GHz Kryo 465 Silver)</li>\r\n<li><strong>GPU</strong>: Adreno 618</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Memory</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Card slot</strong>: microSDXC (dedicated slot)</li>\r\n<li><strong>Internal</strong>: 128GB, 8GB RAM</li>\r\n<li>UFS 2.1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Main Camera</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Quad</strong>: 48 MP, f/1.7, 26mm (wide), 1/2.0\", 0.8&micro;m, PDAF</li>\r\n<li>8 MP, f/2.2, 119˚ (ultrawide), 1/4.0\", 1.12&micro;m</li>\r\n<li>2 MP, f/2.4, (macro)</li>\r\n<li>2 MP, f/2.4, (depth)</li>\r\n<li><strong>Features</strong>: LED flash, HDR, panorama</li>\r\n<li><strong>Video</strong>: 4K@30fps, 1080p@30fps</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Selfie Camera</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Single</strong>: 32 MP, f/2.4, 26mm (wide), 1/2.8\", 0.8&micro;m</li>\r\n<li><strong>Features</strong>: HDR</li>\r\n<li><strong>Video</strong>: 1080p@30fps</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Sound</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Loudspeaker</strong>: Yes</li>\r\n<li><strong>3.5mm jack</strong>: Yes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Communications</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>WLAN</strong>: Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, dual-band, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot</li>\r\n<li><strong>Bluetooth</strong>: 5.0, A2DP, LE</li>\r\n<li><strong>GPS</strong>: Yes, with A-GPS, GLONASS, GALILEO, BDS</li>\r\n<li><strong>Radio</strong>: FM radio</li>\r\n<li><strong>USB</strong>: 2.0, Type-C 1.0 reversible connector, USB On-The-Go</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Sensors</strong>: Fingerprint (under Display, optical), accelerometer, gyro, proximity, compass</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Battery</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Non-removable Li-Po 4015 mAh Battery</li>\r\n<li><strong>Charging</strong>: Fast charging 30W</li>\r\n<li>VOOC 4.0</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL),
(208, 189, 'ar', 'Samsung Galaxy S21+ - 6.7-inch 256GB/8GB Dual SIM 5G Mobile Phone - Phantom Violet', '<p><img src=\"/storage/media/0rSWd4rgyqg7KjW8Cxizer02Mrca0citsT6mY38U.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"970\" height=\"450\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>The fastest chip ever in Galaxy</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"/storage/media/4Ba4h6HRIkO65H2iGjra6jQykPw5a1xt8Lux6aZm.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"970\" height=\"450\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Witness the fastest chip ever in a Galaxy. With a 5nm processor on board, you get seamless multitasking and hyper-fast content streaming.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/storage/media/pk8IcAWeUqLA9ihNE8YkqolplYG6IebPT1MdbDDi.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"350\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Contour Cut Camera Design</strong></p>\r\n<p>The real metal finish on the main camera adds unity to the design and accentuates the luxury of the haze texture. It&rsquo;s an iconic new camera design made to turn heads.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/storage/media/C5vqqNRCOkt1YKh6ShBIMmlyEq0SrL3Y0nHQQl7u.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"350\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Intelligent Battery</strong></p>\r\n<p>Power through your day. And then more.</p>\r\n<p>*Galaxy S21 5G\'s battery is big and smart, learning your app usage style to optimise power consumption.</p>\r\n<p><strong>8K Video</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"/storage/media/aevwN979pH1SQYIAwsjkT9XI5ClpPoPyaXTius5S.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"970\" height=\"450\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Get cinema quality video in the palm of your hands. Capture incredible detail in 8K resolution with super smooth action at 24 frames per second.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/storage/media/ltmsk8lMaOzLVBQduByIjmXG9F0lZXlUDDL7l7yb.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"350\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>High Resolution</strong></p>\r\n<p>Get amazingly clear, high-quality photos with the large 64MP sensor.*</p>\r\n<p>*Even in dark situations, it takes in plenty of light to get the rich image quality. It&rsquo;s all in the details.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/storage/media/pndK3FEKU55JoJyMlyckzBqkkIh3vog7fbv7UADN.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"449\" height=\"350\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Space Zoom</strong></p>\r\n<p>With Hybrid Optic Zoom and enhanced Super Resolution you can zoom up to 30X^*^ with clarity and precision. And the new Zoom Lock helps stabilise your shots.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dynamic AMOLED 2X</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"/storage/media/ZHNEPmH7BWudQPPykmOy3ttB8tLqedlR7UwTdvKO.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"970\" height=\"450\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Unbelievably bright. Incredibly vivid. Surprisingly smooth. That&rsquo;s precisely the viewing experience you&rsquo;ll get with the Dynamic AMOLED 2X, even under bright sunlight! Thanks to our Eye Comfort Shield, it even intelligently adjusts blue light so your eyes won\'t feel so tired.</p>\r\n<h2>Technical Specifications:</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Network</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Technology</strong>: GSM / CDMA / HSPA / EVDO / LTE / 5G</li>\r\n<li><strong>2G bands</strong>: GSM 850 / 900 / 1800 / 1900 - SIM 1 &amp; SIM 2 (Dual SIM model only) CDMA 800 / 1900 &amp; TD-SCDMA</li>\r\n<li><strong>3G bands</strong>: HSDPA 850 / 900 / 1700(AWS) / 1900 / 2100 CDMA2000 1xEV-DO</li>\r\n<li><strong>4G bands</strong>: LTE</li>\r\n<li><strong>5G bands</strong>: SA/NSA/Sub6/mmWave</li>\r\n<li><strong>Speed</strong>: HSPA 42.2/5.76 Mbps, LTE-A (CA), 5G</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Body</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Dimensions</strong>: 161.4 x 75.6 x 7.8 mm</li>\r\n<li><strong>Weight</strong>: 202 g</li>\r\n<li><strong>Build</strong>: Glass front (Gorilla Glass Victus), plastic back, aluminum frame</li>\r\n<li><strong>SIM</strong>: Dual SIM (Nano-SIM, dual stand-by)</li>\r\n<li>IP68 dust/water resistant (up to 1.5m for 30 mins)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Display</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Type</strong>: Dynamic AMOLED 2X, 120Hz, HDR10+, 1300 nits (peak)</li>\r\n<li><strong>Size</strong>: 6.7 inches, 107.8 cm2 (~88.4% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n<li><strong>Resolution</strong>: 1080 x 2400 pixels, 20:9 ratio (~394 ppi density)</li>\r\n<li><strong>Protection</strong>: Corning Gorilla Glass Victus</li>\r\n<li>HDR10+</li>\r\n<li>Always-on Display</li>\r\n<li>120Hz (up to FHD resolution)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Platform</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>OS</strong>: Android 11, One UI 3.1</li>\r\n<li><strong>Chipset</strong>: Exynos 2100 (5 nm)</li>\r\n<li><strong>CPU</strong>: Octa-core (1x2.90 GHz Cortex-X1 and 3x2.80 GHz GHz Cortex-A78 and 4x2.20 GHz Cortex-A55)</li>\r\n<li><strong>GPU</strong>: Mali-G78 MP14</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Memory</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Card slot</strong>: No</li>\r\n<li><strong>Internal</strong>: 256GB ROM, 8GB RAM</li>\r\n<li>UFS 3.1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Main Camera</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Triple</strong>: 12 MP, f/1.8, 26mm (wide), 1/1.76\", 1.8&micro;m, Dual Pixel PDAF, OIS<br />64 MP, f/2.0, 28mm (telephoto), 1/1.76\", 0.8&micro;m, PDAF, OIS, 1.1x optical zoom, 3x hybrid zoom<br />12 MP, f/2.2, 13mm, 120˚ (ultrawide), 1/2.55\" 1.4&micro;m, Super Steady video</li>\r\n<li><strong>Features</strong>: LED flash, auto-HDR, panorama</li>\r\n<li><strong>Video</strong>: 8K@30fps, 4K@30/60fps, 1080p@30/60/120fps, 720p@960fps, HDR10+, stereo sound rec., gyro-EIS &amp; OIS</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Selfie Camera</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Single</strong>: 10 MP, f/2.2, 26mm (wide), 1/3.24\", 1.22&micro;m, Dual Pixel PDAF</li>\r\n<li><strong>Features</strong>: Dual video call, Auto-HDR</li>\r\n<li><strong>Video</strong>: 4K@30/60fps, 1080p@30fps</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Sound</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Loudspeaker</strong>: Yes, with stereo speakers</li>\r\n<li><strong>3.5mm jack</strong>: No</li>\r\n<li>32-bit/384kHz audio</li>\r\n<li>Tuned by AKG</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Communications</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>WLAN</strong>: Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac/6e, dual-band, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot</li>\r\n<li><strong>Bluetooth</strong>: 5.0, A2DP, LE</li>\r\n<li><strong>GPS</strong>: Yes, with A-GPS, GLONASS, BDS, GALILEO</li>\r\n<li><strong>NFC</strong>: Yes</li>\r\n<li><strong>Radio</strong>: No</li>\r\n<li><strong>USB</strong>: USB Type-C 3.2, USB On-The-Go</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Sensors</strong>: Fingerprint (under display, ultrasonic), accelerometer, gyro, proximity, compass, barometer</li>\r\n<li>ANT+</li>\r\n<li>Bixby natural language commands and dictation</li>\r\n<li>Samsung DeX, Samsung Wireless DeX (desktop experience support)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Battery</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Non-removable Li-Po 4800 mAh Battery</li>\r\n<li><strong>Charging</strong>: Fast Battery charging 25W</li>\r\n<li>USB Power Delivery 3.0</li>\r\n<li>Fast Qi/PMA wireless charging 15W</li>\r\n<li>Reverse wireless charging 4.5W</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL),
