(218, 199, 'ar', 'Nillikin Bumper Leather Case For Apple IPad Pro 12.9 (2020) - Black', '<ul>\r\n<li>Nillkin Bumper Leather cover case for Apple iPad Pro 12.9 (2020)</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Made from imported TPU, PC, and PU material, the Nillkin bumper provides your iPad with triple protection. The geometric design molded by integral injection gives a subtle, yet elegant appearance while providing optimal protection.</li>\r\n<li>Nillkin Bumper features a flip cover made from a special PU leather with a dot texture design, making it durable and slip-resistant. It features an in-built magnet connection which integrates with the iPad&rsquo;s auto-sleep/wake feature. The flip cover has a unique design that lets you place your iPad at any angle while typing, reading, or browsing the web.</li>\r\n<li>Nillkin bumper provides additional protection around the corners. Bumpers located on each corner protect your iPad from bumps and scratches. It also features a holder for your iPad pen.</li>\r\n<li>Imported leather material</li>\r\n<li>Made with a durable PU leather finish with a diamond texture for a comfortable grip preventing slips.</li>\r\n<li>Reliable protection</li>\r\n<li>Double protection with a combination of PC back panel and TPU border.</li>\r\n<li>All-round protection</li>\r\n<li>The case is bump and impact-resistant with bumpers on all four corners.</li>\r\n<li>Transparent back panel</li>\r\n<li>A crystal clear back panel protects while allowing a transparent view of the unique iPad design.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL),
